volume.name: Ugly Is As Ugly Does Broom-Hilda

description: The German translation of Uncle Sam

It's the shocking final showdown between the Superior Spider-Man and the maniac known as Massacre!

By Dan Slott and Giuseppe Camuncoli.

Plus: Electro returns and he doesn't just want revenge on Thor... he's out to kill the Thunder God! Only Spider-Man can stop him!

By Christopher Yost and Marco Checchetto.

Also: It’s the startling conclusion to Spider-Man Noir: Eyes Without A Face! The brutal and relentless Crime Master is the least of Spider-Man’s concerns! As the bloody wave of violent crime spreads across the city, Peter Parker discovers the greater monster is the eminent biologist, Dr. Otto Octavius! If Spider-Man lives to escape the grisly clutches of New York’s most dangerous killer, will he survive a final encounter against the heartless, death-dealing scientist?

By David Hine, Fabrice Sapolsky and Carmine Di Giandomenico.

Collects:

  • Superior Spider-Man #5
  • Avenging Spider-Man #18
  • Spider-Man Noir: Eyes Without A Face #4

The X-Men and the Avengers have both felt the power of the Phoenix – and the world will never be the same again!

By Jonathan Hickman, Olivier Coipel, Kieron Gillen and Billy Tan.

Includes material reprinted from: Uncanny X-Men #13-14 and Avengers vs X-Men #6.

Daredevil has been stripped of all his senses! How can he possibly escape the kingdom of Doctor Doom?!

By Mark Waid and Chris Samnee.

Also: Misty Knight assembles the Black Panther, Paladin and Silver Sable to battle the Villains for Hire!

By Dan Abnett, Andy Lanning and Renato Arlem.

Plus: The young mutants from Utopia are brought to Avengers Academy! Whose side will X-23 take?

By Christos Gage and Tom Grummett.

Includes material reprinted from: Daredevil #15, Villains for Hire #0.1 and Avengers Academy #29-30.
